{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63e3ddcee0","title":"为问候胡志明致刘少奇电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"962b804618","index":0,"year":1950,"month":2,"day":1,"articleId":"63e3ddcee0"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"5d02fe744e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡志明，越南民主共和国主席兼总理。这时正在北京。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9ab3040c53","type":"title","text":"为问候胡志明致刘少奇电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"},{"id":"5d02fe744e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"},{"id":"a075dc16fa","type":"paragraph","text":"请替我们问候胡志明同志，他在为越南民族独立与建立越南人【民】民主政权的英勇斗争中起了领导者与组织者的作用。中越两国已互相承认，并即将建立外交关系，苏联已承【认】越南，其他各新民主国家估计亦可能承认（越南请求各国承认并建立外交关系的申明文件，我驻苏大使馆已为转达各新民主国家的驻苏使馆）。我们为越南加入以苏联为首的反帝民主大家庭致深切的庆贺，并祝越南全境统一早日实现，胡志明同志及其战友们身体健康。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"},{"id":"fa67c71ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"},{"id":"a8028c0364","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"},{"id":"3e5bc75099","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年二月一日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0"}],"page":{"id":"5898955c12","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"63e3ddcee0","start":189,"end":189}}}},"__N_SSG":true}